								If you're interested in joining The Crimson Sky Empire in Star Wars Galaxies simply introduce yourself to us here with a simple application. Keep in mind we are an Imperial PA, we do NOT accept Rebels, and our Player Association is located on the Flurry server on Tatooine, in the city of Bestine.<BR><BR>To become a member of CSE you must find a full guild member to sponsor you, and pass a review by the guild membership. If your application is accepted and you've been added to the guild as a recruit you will have 2-4 WEEKS in which time to prove yourself, if by that time you have not found a member to sponsor your trial period as a recruit will be over and we'll part ways.<BR><BR>The Guildmaster, Officers, and CSE members who have socialized and adventured with you will decide whether you are CSE material. At any time during your evaluation you are expected to act as a full member, and at any point during your 2-4 week trial you may be promoted to full membership when it has been decided that you have proven yourself. If for some reason you are not promoted, please understand it's nothing personal and we only want a good fit for us and you, hence the trial period before making any commitment.<BR><BR>Being a member of CSE means you understand what is expected of you. Please read the About CSE pages in full as you will be held accountable to the rules and guidelines written there. <BR><BR>To make the best use of our limited time to find our more about yourself and your character(s), please post full details and anything else that is relevant to why you would make a good addition to our guild.<BR><BR><b>Current Guild Application Requirements: *NEW*</b><BR><BR><b>OPEN APPLICATIONS ARE CLOSED</b><BR>You may still apply to join the SWG Faction, however you will need to find (2) Crimson Sky Empire Members to sponsor you, or a Guild Recruiter before your application is accepted.<BR><BR>You must already have earned 200 Imperial Faction Points, and declared as a Covert Imperial Faction member. By declaring you are showing your intentions and support of fellow declared guild members.<BR><BR>You must post a new message in the recruitment forum using the format supplied below with your Character name, Profession, and various other details to let us know more about you.<BR><BR>You must be ACTIVE in-game, and pro-active about getting to know our members, join hunts, pvp events, work with guild crafters, etc. Only in select cases will applications be extended if you apply and disapear shortly after or members cannot vouch for your activity and impressions of your demeanor.<BR><BR><b>Recruit Rights:</b><BR>After being guilded and given the title of Recruit you have the right of a review by guild peers and officers by 4 weeks of your application post (or from the day you were guilded as a recruit). If there has been any oversight which may have led to no review or announcement of whether you have been accepted as a full member or denied, it is your right to formally request one to the faction GM or a recruitment Officer. Your review will immediately be launched and an answer will be given within 1 week.<BR><BR><b>Members that sponsor applicants:</b> If you decide to sponsor an applicant, please post on the private member forum stating so and a review of the recruit will be started for open comments by other members. CSE Members may not sponsor more than 2 applicants at a time, and must seek fellow guildmates to sponsor additional prospective members<BR><BR>----------<BR><BR>Please copy and paste the following into your <b>NEW</b> message posted in the Guild Recruiting forum.<BR><BR>----------<BR><BR><b>Character Name(s):</b><BR>* This is required, your application will be deleted if you do not provide names of your characters on the flurry server. If you have multiple accounts and characters please provide those here as well. Please note we do not allow members of this faction to join our guild while a member of another guild/PA with different characters. Your commitment and activity with our guild must be a priority and not divided.<BR><BR><b>Professions:</b><BR>List your current professions or skills here. Are you an Artisian? If so are you a Armorcrafter, Weaponcrafter, and how far along are you skillwise? Are you a Master Marksman? Do you plan being a Smuggler, etc, list it here.<BR><BR><b>Player versus Player:</b> [ ] Yes  [ ] No<BR>Do you intend to participate in PvP, or in Battlefields?<BR><BR><b>Imperial Faction:</b> [ ] Yes  [ ] No<BR>Do you intend to join the Imperial Faction as a Covert and declare your loyalty to the Empire?<BR><BR><b>Tell us a little about yourself:</b><BR><BR><b>What interested you in our Guild?:</b><BR><BR><b>What expectations do you have of our Guild?:</b><BR>                  
									<b><br><br>-------------------------<br></b>
									<b>Seira - Creature Handler/Bio Engineer/Pistoleer/Medic</b><BR><img src="http://www.crimsonsky.com/images/signatures/seira_black.gif"> 
